{"api_version": "2022-08-31", "model_id": "bc2-1page-cleveland-narrative", "content": "Original Narrative\nTitle: ASSAULT // NAMED SUSPECT\nOn 12/31/2017 at approximately 1217 hours received information from victim who states he was jumped and knocked to the ground after a verbal argument at Moe's Tire Center (8202 Superior) by owner's son (NS). Victim states doing numerous business dealings with owner in past and victim states attempting to sell (4) used tires for $20 to $30 to named suspect.\nOwner's son (NS) stated his father was not at store. Victim states named suspect began calling him \"racial terms\" and a \"crack head\", stating he wouldn't purchase tires and \"get the hell out\". Victim states during verbal argument, named suspect came from behind the counter and attempted to hit him. Victim states striking named suspect and then named suspect throwing himto the ground. Victim states (4) other employees held himon the ground until police arrived. . 3S13 SGT BEITEL and 3S14 SGT HAYES on scene . Medic #1 treated/released\n. NS made an Assault/Named Suspect report also (SEE related RMS #2017-414726\n. Advised to prosecutor\n. Unit: 3C14 . Typed by SDCO Hess #2017-414738 12/31/2017\nYou created this PDF from an application that is not licensed to print to novaPDF printer (http://www.novapdf.com)", "languages": [], "pages": [{"page_number": 8, "angle": null, "width": 8.5, "height": 11.0, "unit": "inch", "lines": [{"content": "Original Narrative", "polygon": [{"x": 0.3247, "y": 0.3724}, {"x": 1.8576, "y": 0.3724}, {"x": 1.8624, "y": 0.5634}, {"x": 0.3247, "y": 0.5729}], "spans": [{"offset": 0, "length": 18}]}, {"content": "Title: ASSAULT // NAMED SUSPECT", "polygon": [{"x": 0.3152, "y": 0.9978}, {"x": 2.6551, "y": 0.9978}, {"x": 2.6551, "y": 1.1458}, {"x": 0.3152, "y": 1.1506}], "spans": [{"offset": 19, "length": 31}]}, {"content": "On 12/31/2017 at approximately 1217 hours received information from victim who states he was jumped and knocked to the ground", "po